{"tid":1638902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆唔知點解好鍾意睇陳怡","createTime":"2019-10-08T12:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T18:01:19.000Z","uid":202342,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ff94cdd5817732f605d0656fa6d67a54a9eb77c2","tid":1638902,"uid":202342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"自問我老豆平時係個幾nice既人<br />\n有fd上到黎都會同佢地有講有笑咁<br />\n但偏偏佢就係個藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自呢幾個月既運動以黎已經同佢講過好多次究竟宜家係發生緊咩事<br />\n佢都係堅持香港就係大陸既一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大陸想你點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一講唔過我就係：我唔識得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又問我出去有幾錢收<br />\n宜家重要成日睇陳怡個八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重要可以一睇就睇幾個鐘<br />\n個八婆發表埋自己d偉倫 顛倒是非黑白 一聽到佢把閪聲我就燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排同佢接近一句野都冇講過 費事嗌交<br />\n唔該陳怡你個垃圾收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日係度荼毒人 又唔諗下會有人真係信<br />\n借今次個反送中運動上位 吸納藍絲做觀衆 我屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問咁多位手足究竟我應該點做"},{"pid":"3df6a491cdfc15c770783d5109f35b8332380516","tid":1638902,"uid":18581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"可能你老竇好呢味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d440a2a97569ca680c458e234ce57da66eecf2","tid":1638902,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"我哥都係。。"},{"pid":"50e77f0ca611ad53ffae872dbdba6cb384b68a5b","tid":1638902,"uid":268959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5d440a2a97569ca680c458e234ce57da66eecf2","tid":1638902,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"我哥都係。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下咩age咁重口